== 意外事件 ==
2007年，胡安安在[[橫店影視城|橫店影視城]]拍攝電視劇《[[亂世豪門|亂世豪門]]》的強暴戲時，遭[[中國大陸|大陸]][[臨時演員|臨時演員]]侵犯，導致胯下瘀青<ref>[http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/Chinatimes/ExteriorContent/Showbiz/Showbiz-Page/0,4434,content+110511+112007062500556,00.html 許安安哭訴輪暴戲遭硬來] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071114234530/http://showbiz.chinatimes.com/Chinatimes/ExteriorContent/Showbiz/Showbiz-Page/0,4434,content+110511+112007062500556,00.html |date=2007-11-14 }}</ref>。

